| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2473 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9a06f5f4-e022-567d-9988-791103e9d3a6"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
